{
  "stem": "6966.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the coach were already some Jewish people and a six-foot-tall young Nazi, a swastika band around his arm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as we got in, he told me, sit down and quiet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We sat down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that went from street to street, collecting Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when the coach was full, off we went through the streets, across the River Maas, on the other side of the Maas, of the river, it stopped on a piece of land.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on that land stood some large wooden huts, formerly used for goods from America, Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in front of Hut 24, [SPEAKING DUTCH]-- that's Dutch for Hut 24, which it's called now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After 50 years, Rotterdam is coming to their senses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We must do something about remembering the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We stood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The coach stopped before that hut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Our luggage was slung out on the floor, on the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to pick them up and carry them inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as I came in, I saw hundreds of Jewish families, a lot of people I knew, and also about four or five SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I went to one of them and showed him my birth certificate and said to them, I'm English, and Swiss consul letter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He waved them away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Showed them one when you go to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Westerbork is the transit camp in the north of Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] So we were wandering around among the people, saying hello to friends I knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still see the sad faces.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being on the committee of the, of the Jewish club, which had all the families, I still see the sad faces of people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't know what to do, taken out of the homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to leave everything behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
